174 A.3d 514 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. JAMES T. PRITCHETT, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-158 September Term 2017

079343 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003761-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
